3C. Congestion Weight Formula [ADDED]
Reason: Dijkstra and A* need a consistent formula to convert
flow/capacity ratios into travel time multipliers.

  travel_time(minutes) = (distance / speed) * 60 * congestion_factor

  congestion_ratio = flow / capacity
  if ratio >= 0.90 -> congestion_factor = 3.0  (severe)
  if ratio >= 0.75 -> congestion_factor = 1.8  (moderate)
  if ratio <  0.75 -> congestion_factor = 1.0  (clear)
--------------------------------------------------------


